  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5050692">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5050692/" class="title-link">挺起我的脊梁</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5050692"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiaoxiaoyu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u40266835-16.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jiaoxiaoyu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">米周</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-08-04"
      class="main-meta">2011-08-04 22:48:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5050692_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  如果让我这个历史初中水平的人回忆曾经受过的历史教育，会发现整个体系中，关于抗日的细节大多数都是红色而非蓝色的。在这个全民的历史水平基本都为初中水平的社会里，相信有我这种感觉的人不该占少数。而我们似乎从来都没有觉得这种红蓝之分在叙述抗战历史的时候有什么不妥。...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5050692_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5050692_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










